hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3ceb6717d9ae66bed0d758511aca0e7f903e5a","tid":250342,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:29:51.000Z","msg":"買國產錶有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n我屌哂你地班盲反！"},{"pid":"40e0e254dbfaeceebcd2a3aeb39e00e15168d211","tid":250342,"uid":34155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買錶都比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔試下海鷗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算啦。小朋友係咁。由佢地盲反。我怕佢精工5仔都買唔起。<br />\n<br />\n其實我貪得意咋。單純見佢*上海*中文字logo 幾有情懷feel。<br />\n<br />\n班柒頭一定拎隻casio同我講情懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc78afc1d93b5b2820b599120be6f3a7d806593","tid":250342,"uid":19927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇撚鳩。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc93b2185268a8c0bbab222edd9136ad98346cb","tid":250342,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買錶都比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解唔試下海鷗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n算啦。小朋友係咁。由佢地盲反。我怕佢精工5仔都買唔起。<br />\n<br />\n其實我貪得意咋。單純見佢*上海*中文字logo 幾有情懷feel。<br />\n<br />\n班柒頭一定拎隻casio同我講情懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸人梗係覺得有情懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8a8d5a9803d9d6b14878c01464e541b3a603b3","tid":250342,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:10:49.000Z","msg":"買唔係問題，但話大陸錶有情懷真係on9到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到一兩隻當玩具玩下傷肝，但收藏就免喇，呢啲一世都無咩機會升到值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f913de866fb9b1bf7de854507610a811dc92133","tid":250342,"uid":34155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買唔係問題，但話大陸錶有情懷真係on9到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到一兩隻當玩具玩下傷肝，但收藏就免喇，呢啲一世都無咩機會升到值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收藏一定要升值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好on9啦小朋友。<br />\n大把人買一堆模型 錶 鞋 畫 咩興趣喜好都好。為左升值為左賣？笑撚死人咩。<br />\n收藏 同 投資 都唔撚識分 番去讀多次小學啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n情懷你理撚得我乜柒情懷呀。<br />\n我淨係見隻錶面有中文字做logo。<br />\n錢多買下關你撚事咩。<br />\n玩唔起錶咪出番去囉。<br />\n<br />\n你自己都讀十鳩幾年書用中文啦。<br />\n起碼我櫃入面幾隻勞都無中文字logo啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買下唔同款式又得罪你呀on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261eddfbc1d5eb4581f95d054a4690ab375168ba","tid":250342,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:38:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇撚鳩。</blockquote><br />\n論點？"},{"