ji\" /> <br />\n都話左呢啲一日慢分幾鐘既大陸錶收一兩隻玩下無問題，前面都講左玩，後面講收藏，梗係講收藏投資啦，唔通講返一樣既野咩，中文一詞多意，logic 都無，而家啲連登仔質素真係差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979a91d958646e110d06813364676ee2658d354b","tid":250342,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買唔係問題，但話大陸錶有情懷真係on9到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到一兩隻當玩具玩下傷肝，但收藏就免喇，呢啲一世都無咩機會升到值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收藏一定要升值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好on9啦小朋友。<br />\n大把人買一堆模型 錶 鞋 畫 咩興趣喜好都好。為左升值為左賣？笑撚死人咩。<br />\n收藏 同 投資 都唔撚識分 番去讀多次小學啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n情懷你理撚得我乜柒情懷呀。<br />\n我淨係見隻錶面有中文字做logo。<br />\n錢多買下關你撚事咩。<br />\n玩唔起錶咪出番去囉。<br />\n<br />\n你自己都讀十鳩幾年書用中文啦。<br />\n起碼我櫃入面幾隻勞都無中文字logo啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買下唔同款式又得罪你呀on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港夠有出錶喇，又唔撚鳩見你問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見有兩隻中文字就話情懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌你老母喇，你係情懷既定義係咩都唔識呀，學人話情懷，人唔笑狗都吠啦<img src=\"/a